issue.title: Cleanup
issue.body:
If any of you want to review these changes, I'll keep my PR's up for a few days before merging them.

I mostly cleaned up the code's format and the project's folder structure.
I also changed a bunch of functions to be synchronously instead of asynchronously designed. It makes it easier to read and doesn't impact performance (I think)
